Interface ListIterator

All Known Implementing Classes:
LinkedList.LinkedListIterator
public interface ListIterator

A list iterator allows access of a position in a linked list. This interface contains a subset of the methods of the standard java.util.ListIterator interface. The methods for backward traversal are not included.
